{"pin":"BH02777","subcodes":[{"code":"BH02777","anchor":"","first_line":"Glorified art Thou, O my God! I beseech Thee by Thy grandeur, through which all things have derived their greatness, and by the effulgent lights of Thy countenance [3.5s]... ...O my God and my Master! I am Thy servant and the son of Thy servant. I have risen from my couch","first_line_orig":"سبحانک اللهم یا الهی اسئلک بعظمتک التی منها استعظم کل شیء و بانوار وجهک  ","language":"Ara","word_count":"320","subjects":"@prayer for protection, @transcendence; unknowability of God, @prayer for spiritual recognition, @power and sovereignty of God; omnipotence of God, @detachment; severance; renunciation; patience, @prayer for nearness to God, @the Word of God; influence and centrality of","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#271\"\u003eLL#271\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#470\"\u003eLL#470\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"pm","type_name":"Prayers \u0026 Meditations","language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"type":"pm","type_name":"Prayers \u0026 Meditations","language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"type":"pm","type_name":"Prayers \u0026 Meditations","language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"type":"pm","type_name":"Prayers \u0026 Meditations","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"pm","type_name":"Prayers \u0026 Meditations","language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"type":"pm","type_name":"Prayers \u0026 Meditations","language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"}]},{"code":"BH02777RIS","anchor":"ris","translations":[{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"